1. *Zveri* su često prikazivane u filmovima i serijama. (Beasts are often depicted in movies and TV shows.)
2. Lovci su čuli neobične zvukove *zveri* u noći. (Hunters heard unusual sounds of beasts at night.)
3. *Zveri* u šumi su uvek opasne za ljude. (Beasts in the forest are always dangerous for people.)
4. Deca su bila uplašena kad su videla veliku *zver* u dvorištu. (Children were frightened when they saw a big beast in the yard.)
5. U starim pričama, *zver* se često predstavlja kao simbol tame i zla. (In old tales, a beast is often portrayed as a symbol of darkness and evil.)
6. Neki ljudi smatraju da su *zveri* inteligentnije od ljudi. (Some people believe that beasts are more intelligent than humans.)
7. *Zverima* je potrebna sloboda kretanja u prirodi. (Beasts need freedom of movement in nature.)
8. Među najopasnijim *zverima* u Srbiji su vukovi i medvedi. (Among the most dangerous beasts in Serbia are wolves and bears.)
9. Pogledao je u oči *zveri* koja je stajala ispred njega. (He looked into the eyes of the beast that stood in front of him.)
10. Mladić je hrabro krenuo u šumu da bi se suočio sa *zverima*. (The young man bravely went into the forest to confront the beasts.)